  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Marche&apos;s earthquake: give kids a new civic center</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Caldarola is an Italian municipality which is still trying to recover after the serious damages caused by the earthquake that hit Central Italy in 2016. The aim of the project is that of supporting and promoting the rebirth of community life through the rebuilding of a center that can host activities, events, and workshops. Children and young people, in particular, will have a safe place where to meet and stay together, refinding hope and trust in their territory again.</narrative>
  </description>
